reviewText: Can't believe they canceled this show it was great!

Okay, I have friends who think this series is awful. I only got hooked because I viewed two shows on an airplane where I was bored enough to try it. Personally, I think it's great. I, too, had thought "What could be funny about a person with an identity disorder?" but (a) Toni Collette is amazing and (b) what can I say? It's funny. Yep, sad moments, but it's a crazy world out there. Naturally, the DVDs arrived quickly and in perfect order - as usual with Amazon.

One of SHOWTIMES BEST!  Love This show...  Watched the whole season in one weekend!
 A++++
John Presutti
